I'm now designing the dedicated \"Sign Out\" button for the topbar. I've confirmed that `lucide-react` includes a `LogOut` icon. My plan involves integrating this prominent button alongside the user avatar for clear accessibility. I'm verifying the necessary imports within `components/private-app/sidebar-topbar.tsx` to streamline the process. I am focused on the visual placement and design of the sign-out button within the topbar. I am also planning the design plan as requested.\n\n\n\n**Crafting Restricted Access Views**\n\nI'm now focused on delivering a premium UI for restricted access scenarios. My aim is to create custom \"Enclave Clearance Expired\" and \"Clearance Level Insufficient\" screens. These will guide users gracefully with interactive elements, replacing generic errors. I will ensure a high-fidelity look and feel that aligns with GFF AI's design language, offering clear workspace switching options.\n\n\n"}}
