{"ts":"2026-06-27T08:22:33.866Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_end","contentType":"reasoning","reasoning":"**Revising Imports and Adding**\n\nI'm currently updating the import statements as specified, specifically on lines 5-8. I'm swapping the lucide-react imports and then adding `clearPreviewSession` from the preview-auth library. Next, I plan to move forward with the De action.\n\n\n**Implementing Sign Out Button**\n\nI've decided to incorporate a sign-out button right above the clock in the sidebar. I'm replacing the existing SECURE CLOCK section with a button that, when clicked, will clear the preview session and redirect the user to the login portal. This functionality is being achieved using `clearPreviewSession` and `window.location.href`, as I'm adding a button with the LogOut icon and styling it for visual appeal.\n\n\n**Adding Deauthentication Button**\n\nI've integrated the deauthentication button into the top bar, replacing the WorkspaceCommandButton, RoleSwitcherPreview, and Notification components for now. The button, using the `LogOut` icon, is styled and functions to clear the session and redirect to the login portal. This implementation uses `clearPreviewSession` and `window.location.href`, as before.\n\n\n**Integrating Sign Out Action**\n\nI've just added a quick sign-out action, incorporating a sign-out button. This button sits beside the existing components in the top bar. When clicked, it calls `clearPreviewSession` and redirects to the login portal. It's styled for a cohesive look using a red theme. The button replaces the existing components.\n\n\n"}}
